    </div>
    <div class="legacy-content">
      <span class="label reveal">Our Legacy</span>
      <h2 class="legacy-heading reveal reveal-delay-1">
        A church that has<br>stood through <em>history.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="legacy-body reveal reveal-delay-2">
        Founded in 1900 by a group of Black Christians in Montgomery, Alabama, Hutchinson has been more than a church — it has been a refuge, a force for justice, and a home for generations of believers across more than a century.
      </p>

      <div class="legacy-timeline reveal reveal-delay-2" aria-label="Church history timeline">
        <div class="timeline-track-h" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="timeline-items">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">1900</div>
            <p class="timeline-desc">Hutchinson founded — a faithful witness in Montgomery.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">1957</div>
            <p class="timeline-desc">Church bombed after serving as a Mass Meeting site in the Movement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">1987</div>
            <p class="timeline-desc">Renamed Hutchinson Missionary Baptist Church (HMBC).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2023</div>
            <p class="timeline-desc">Rev. Cameron R. Thomas begins as pastor — a new season.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legacy-callout reveal">
        <span class="callout-year">1957</span>
        <p class="callout-text">
          During the Montgomery Bus Boycott, Hutchinson served as a gathering site for Mass Meetings. Because of its role in the Civil Rights Movement, the church was bombed in the early hours of January 10th — a testament to the cost and courage of its congregation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="#mission" class="arrow-link reveal">Our Mission &nbsp;→</a>
    </div>
  </section>

